{"tid":1602480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"929臺港大遊行(已落幕)","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:30:39.000Z","uid":304834,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe724deed7fdc142166bf6467ae264f883adac4","tid":1602480,"uid":304834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"天空出現兩道彩虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4eMzbj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4eMzbj.jpg&h=d6a183e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"f9b7afec7998d82a7721b2a98d11c4283445ceee","tid":1602480,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"個天好靚"},{"pid":"ab123477a76268dcae892d30c5ad811dc41b199e","tid":1602480,"uid":304834,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"人生首場集會遊行<br />\n雨很大但人還是很多(超過十萬)<br />\n未避免打到別人盡量不撐傘<br />\n當主舞臺宣佈遊行開始，全體向後轉<br />\n突然成了遊行最前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n途中有港生戴豬嘴排排站，在場臺灣人看了很難過，走過去告訴他們：「這裡是臺灣，可以放心拿下來」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當隊伍遇上中天出訪車行駛路口，令眾人唾口大罵：「製造假新聞、紅媒滾出臺灣」<br />\n還碰見兩位港妹鞋子濕了，臨時換成藍白拖，說是入境隨俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(不愧是臺灣No.1伴手禮)<br />\n<br />\n晚間回到立院前方集合<br />\n兩旁搭建的帳篷正在發放精美海報、複印「香港加油」字樣<br />\n今晚街頭學習粵語的活動(&times;)非常充實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1911b9e5d7136d28758831e8a869012a8f9fc55b","tid":1602480,"uid":327858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edcdcaec73b556faa41bd7e811194f8af31712e","tid":1602480,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"謝謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9293ab374f29c7a42aff3416fac3cfb01a45d39","tid":1602480,"uid":283136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d3ec04fe23d5a77be3dcd8f8ac744b4c74613b","tid":1602480,"uid":205505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:32:25.000Z","msg":"感謝 台灣的朋友支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad3cb9f73442302e2dc9cfab339f66d0396c280","tid":1602480,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"感謝台灣絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494c672e65e8be5fb0a90e1273c3b9f9640b8f3e","tid":1602480,"uid":49191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"感謝 多謝支持"}]}